                    "Achieve financial freedom while maintaining a healthy work-life balance.",
                    "Prioritize opportunities in Singapore, while considering countries with overlapping working hours with Jakarta.",
                    "Earn between USD 100,000 and USD 150,000 annually.",
                    "Increase income to prepare for future family and marriage."
